    <span class="ml-1.5 text-xs font-bold text-foreground tabular-nums">9.5</span>
  </div>
              <span class="text-sm font-heading font-bold text-foreground whitespace-nowrap hidden sm:block">Nemokamai / nuo 10 €/metus</span>
